= Testing the Plugin

Clone the repository and run the tests.

{{{
$ git clone git://github.com/fesplugas/typus.git
$ cd typus
$ rake
}}}

By default tests are be performed against a SQLite3 database in memory. You can 
also run tests against PostgreSQL and MySQL databases. (database name is 
{{{typus_test}}})

{{{
$ rake DB=mysql
$ rake DB=postgresql
}}}
